{"tid":1724732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打開運動嘅新缺口！文宣新方向 和理非快入","createTime":"2019-11-15T14:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T14:32:17.000Z","uid":270673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18f12643b8072e393a54c8f0210dcf9c745473a2","tid":1724732,"uid":270673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BT2dz9Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBT2dz9Z.png&h=fec7138a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共成日用白色恐怖控制我地<br />\n又話流浮山刀手 又話熄燈制水 又話出解放軍<br />\n嚇到淺黄同藍絲俾人牽著鼻子走<br />\n但大家有無諗過<br />\n其實我哋可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反客為主</span></strong><br />\n用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">白色恐怖</span></span></strong>夾啲真野兇鳩番佢哋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如上圖 間中講啲真或者假野分化黑警同藍絲<br />\n例如大綱係講：<br />\n  高層當<strong>前線警condom</strong> 用完會送佢哋死（我相信真係會有...扮高官AO)<br />\n  白警交哂啲黑警罪證去美國 準備<strong>警署放炸彈</strong>一齊死（扮白警）<br />\n  黄絲收買黑社會 準備<strong>大規模搞狗宿</strong>（扮黑社會）<br />\n  政府準備<strong>出賣清算前線黑警</strong> 緩和民意（應該真係會有啦...扮警高層）<br />\n  將會去中資同藍店發放無色無味<strong>殺人氣體</strong>（運用chem知識）......<br />\n創意時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之間中有啲真嘅消息 有啲假消息夾雜<br />\n分化藍絲同黑警嘅團結性<br />\n等佢哋軍心大亂 甚至叛變爭住出賣自己人<br />\n當然講嘅嘢要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">中哂佢哋心理</span></span></strong> 佢哋先會驚：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">人身安全 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">被暴徒批鬥</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">被出賣 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">政府逼害香港人  </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">經濟利益受損</span><br />\n <br />\n而方法可以用大家最叻嘅<br />\n老人文宣 airdrop 自製錄音（參考錄音師） <br />\n最新職業：錄音師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723358</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n去藍絲group扮專業人士講（白警 消防  黑社會 記者 權威藍絲 官媒 化學專家...）<br />\n接觸多藍絲嘅可以直接口述<br />\n一定要係藍絲whatsapp grp同<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多接觸嘅地方廣傳</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中共最叻玩分化<br />\n成效有幾大 相信大家有眼睇<br />\n我地要以其人之道 還治其人之身<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28838ce377764d3b440b690eba8cfa1a1f02809","tid":1724732,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b41f7fb510da99a7cb6d8be88b6be2290bd03f25","tid":1724732,"uid":270673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"ddccfc35a8c08855b930b0acd64af6fde7303698","tid":1724732,"uid":270673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"18b855cf0a7fdcba6c37bbe1012fa2ce6959ffa9","tid":1724732,"uid":270673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"49f19a55e60f96626eff9d430a4be95296674e7e","tid":1724732,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"支持前線自決 外來人唔好再入去！<br />\n收到消息太多鬼混入去叫人留守！"},{"pid":"3f25a524af56fcfa3e492a3366f05fe00433aa82","tid":1724732,"uid":270673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"e30767ee2366395f0b48f4d35a3f2ef7c024a2ab","tid":1724732,"uid":270673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"5c6d216cfde21